e used around the world where you can expand your skillset and work with many different technologies.</span></p></div></div><div class=\"mt-2\"><div><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 inline-block animate-spin rounded-full border-4 border-solid border-black border-t-transparent\"></div></div><!--/$--></div></div><div class=\"mt-8\"><h2 class=\"font-semibold\">Chế độ đãi ngộ</h2><div class=\"mt-2\"><div class=\"pl-0\"><div class=\"prose max-w-full text-sm text-black lg:text-base\"><ul> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">From Monday to Friday</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">International Travel opportunities</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">13th month and productivity bonus</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Free lunch, parking, uniforms</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Yearly company trip</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Healthcare insurance package</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">24/24 Personal Accident insurance</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Free English training programs (Cambridge English Scale) at office</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Continuing development of technical and soft skills through working and formal training</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Trade Union &amp; Staff Social Club - Sport clubs (Yoga, Swimming, Badminton, Football, Gym,...)</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Good working conditions and environment</span></li> </ul></div></div></div></div>','CNGTYTNHHMITEKVITNAM.png','CÔNG TY TNHH MITEK VIỆT NAM',NULL,NULL),(56,'Sari town, số 16 đường số 5, Phường An Lợi Đông, Thành phố Thủ Đức, Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh',NULL,'hoidanit@gmail.com','<div><h2 class=\"mb-2 font-semibold\">Về chúng tôi</h2><div class=\"prose max-w-full leading-snug text-gray-500\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Welcome to Suntek, where creativity meets technology in the dynamic realm of gaming! ? As a cutting-edge game studio and outsourcing powerhouse, Suntek is your passport to an exciting world of innovation and collaboration.</span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">At Suntek, we are more than just a company; we are a community of passionate creators, developers, and visionaries who come together to craft immersive and captivating gaming experiences. Our commitment to pushing the boundaries of what\'s possible in the gaming industry is reflected in every pixel, every line of code, and every idea that comes to life within our studio.</span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">What sets Suntek apart is our relentless pursuit of excellence and a culture that thrives on diversity, collaboration, and a shared love for gaming. As a global leader in game development and outsourcing, we take pride in our ability to seamlessly blend creativity with technical expertise, delivering top-tier solutions that captivate audiences worldwide.</span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Joining Suntek means joining a team that values your unique skills, encourages your innovative spirit, and provides an environment where your career can flourish. Whether you\'re a seasoned developer looking for new challenges or a rising star eager to make your mark, Suntek is the place where your ideas can take flight.</span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Embark on a journey with Suntek and be part of a company that doesn\'t just create games – we craft experiences that leave a lasting impact. Your adventure in the world of gaming starts here!</span></p></div></div><div class=\"mt-8\"><h2 class=\"font-semibold\">Chế độ đãi ngộ</h2><div class=\"mt-2\"><div class=\"pl-0\"><div class=\"prose max-w-full text-sm text-black lg:text-base\"><p>13th-month salary<br/>Review salary once per year<br/>Insurances such as Vietnamese labor law and premium health care<br/>Meal and parking allowances are covered by the company<br/>Exciting company outings/events and team-building activities<br/>Open, friendly, professional working environment, values-driven, and agile culture.<br/>Attractive career path, we focus on your development.<br/>Sponsorship for training courses, and professional certificates<br/>Work-life balance 40-hr per week from Mon to Fri.</p></div></div></div></div>','CNGTYCPHNSUNTEK.png','CÔNG TY CỔ PHẦN SUNTEK',NULL,NULL),(57,'Lầu 9, Etown 3, 364 Cộng Hòa, Phường 13, Quận Tân Bình, Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh',NULL,'hoidanit@gmail.com','<div><h2 class=\"mb-2 font-semibold\">Về chúng tôi</h2><div class=\"prose max-w-full leading-snug text-gray-500\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">NEC established its liaison office in Vietnam in the early 1990s. In line with its growth strategy, it was re-organized as NEC Vietnam Co., Ltd. in 2006, with a newfound commitment to grow the business and contribute towards the people and society of Vietnam.</span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">In a rapidly changing business environment, we have evolved to be a comprehensive solution provider, to deliver on our core strengths of providing Solutions for Society, which involves providing social infrastructure benefiting citizens and communities.</span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Today, we are highly dependent on ICT technologies. We are proud to say that NEC is well-positioned to meet the needs of the market, to have the relevant technologies in-house, and is ready to deliver.</span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">We provide Solutions &amp; Services, including:</span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><strong>1./ Software development (Offshore) for many clients from Japan &amp; APAC Region (Singapore, Malaysia, etc.).</strong></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><strong>2./ System integrator in the field of:</strong></span></p> <ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"> <li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Telecom Carrier Industry</span></li> <li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Retail Industry</span></li> <li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Manufacturing Industry</span></li> <li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Food and Beverage Industry</span></li> <li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><strong>Public Sector (Biometrics on Vietnam National ID, Satellite LOTUSat-1)</strong></span></li> </ul> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><strong>3./ Integrate with own and/or partner solutions.</strong></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><strong>4./ Face Recognition Solution “Smart Face Authentication”.</strong></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Refer to https://www.facebook.com/NECVietnam.page for new chances and do not hesitate to apply to NEC VietNam.</span></p></div></div><div class=\"mt-2\"><div><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 inline-block animate-spin rounded-full border-4 border-solid border-black border-t-transparent\"></div></div><!--/$--></div></div><div class=\"mt-8\"><h2 class=\"font-semibold\">Chế độ đãi ngộ</h2><div class=\"mt-2\"><div class=\"pl-0\"><div class=\"prose max-w-full text-sm text-black lg:text-base\"><p>Working time: Mon-Fri, Hybrid working mode (WFH available)<br/>13th Salary + Year-End Reward (a half month) + Excellent Bonus<br/>Special allowance for foreign language certificate (up to 500USD/month)<br/>Full social package (SI, HI, UI) &amp; Premium healthcare insurance (Aon)<br/>Annual Health Check at the top healthcare center<br/>Up to 19 days of paid leave<br/>Free Japanese class; 1:1 class with native teachers<br/>Udemy account provided &amp; Sponsor examination fee for technical certificates such as AWS, Azure, PMP, etc and get the incentive (up to 10M)<br/>Many company activities to tighten the relationship between employees: Company trip, Year-end Event, Team building, Sports Day, Family Day, Outing Trip, etc.<br/>Reward Most Valuable Player (MVP) for individual &amp; team twice a year<br/>Sport clubs provided (100% sponsored by company): Football, Badminton<br/>Professional environment with clear procedures and good working facilities<br/>Onsite opportunities: short-term and long-term assignments in Japan, and APAC.</p></div></div></div></div>','NECVietnam.png','NEC Vietnam',NULL,NULL),(58,'Tầng 15, Opal Tower, 92 Nguyễn Hữu Cảnh, Phường 22, Quận Bình Thạnh, Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh',NULL,'hoidanit@gmail.com','<div><h2 class=\"mb-2 font-semibold\">Về chúng tôi</h2><div class=\"prose max-w-full leading-snug text-gray-500\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">ALLEXCEED VIETNAM (thành lập 2010) là công ty phát triển phần mềm được thành lập bởi 100% vốn đầu tư của ALLEXCEED JAPAN (thành lập năm 1976). </span></p> <p>Do nhu cầu mở rộng kinh doanh, ALLEXCEED VIETNAM đang cần tuyển một số lượng lớn kỹ sư phát triển phần mềm, cả có kinh nghiệm và chưa có kinh nghiệm cho các dự án của công ty.</p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Gia nhập ALLEXCEED VIETNAM, các bạn sẽ có cơ hội được training đầy đủ các kỹ năng lập trình cũng như các kỹ năng mềm cần thiết trong công việc bởi các kỹ sư có kinh nghiệm dày dặn. Từ đó có thể phát triển năng lực bản 