 Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Norway’s second largest Municipality using our messaging software.</span></li> <li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Worldwide Tire Manufacture using Magento WEB shop delivered by our team.</span></li> </ul> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Netpower was established in 1995, is financially sound and have an ambition to become a leading software company in our area of business.</span></p></div></div><div class=\"mt-2\"><div><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 inline-block animate-spin rounded-full border-4 border-solid border-black border-t-transparent\"></div></div><!--/$--></div></div><div class=\"mt-8\"><h2 class=\"font-semibold\">Chế độ đãi ngộ</h2><div class=\"mt-2\"><div class=\"pl-0\"><div class=\"prose max-w-full text-sm text-black lg:text-base\"><ul> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Opportunity to go work on-site in Norway</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">English Training Program twice a week</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Join dynamic, young, and friendly teams</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">A creative and forward thinking development team to work with</span></li> <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Up to 18 days annual leave which could be converte